[Desktop Entry]
Type=Application
Version=1.0
Name=Disable auto-suspend & lock · live only
Name[zh_CN]=关闭自动休眠和锁屏 · 仅 live
Name[zh_TW]=關閉自動休眠和鎖定 · 僅 live
GenericName=Power
GenericName[zh_CN]=电源
GenericName[zh_TW]=電源
Comment=Keep the machine awake during install (no auto-suspend / screen-off / lock)
Comment[zh_CN]=安装时保持唤醒（不自动休眠 / 熄屏 / 锁屏）
Comment[zh_TW]=安裝時保持喚醒（不自動休眠 / 熄螢幕 / 鎖定）
Exec=/usr/local/bin/gigos-nosleep.sh
Icon=preferences-system-power-management
Terminal=false
StartupNotify=true
Categories=Qt;System;Settings;
X-AppStream-Ignore=true
